Testimonials

Adam C.

My personal training experiences with Aftyn have been nothing short of transformational. When I started working with her I was an out of shape novice who had spent most of my time since the onset of covid parked on the couch watching TV.

Dan R.

I had tried every fad-diet, trendy workout, and God knows what else. It wasn’t until I started training with Aftyn that I really started seeing results. We’ve been working together a year now, and through her incredible enthusiasm and motivation, I have now lost 60 pounds and counting. I would not have been able to accomplish this without her support and depth of knowledge. I’ve learned so much about my body and health from this amazing woman. Thank you Aftyn! Looking forward to another year of working with you!

Shawna L.

    Masks

    With the State’s removal of its mask mandate, Members are no longer required to wear masks the club. Certainly, this is a personal decision and Members can continue wearing a mask should they choose. Our Life Time Team Members will also continue wearing masks at their discretion.

    Guests

    Please refer to your club hours page to view the daily ability for guest visits.

    Health Screening

    To support the health and safety of the entire Life Time community, please remain at home if you're not feeling well..

      About Me

      I took my first group fitness class in 1982 and was immediately hooked! I began teaching classes that same year. 34 years later, I love it more now than ever before. As I Pilates and yoga instructor I feel blessed and inspired every day by the beautiful clients I get to work with. I get a front row seat as I watch them struggle and ultimately succeed. 12 of my clients have been with me for over 5 years. 5 have been with me for a decade.

                        Student Membership Details

                        Discounted monthly rate for individuals at least 12 years of age that are an actively enrolled secondary or post-secondary student. Students receive access to one club from May 1 to August 31. This membership will then automatically convert September 1 to non-access “Student Flex” status at the monthly club flex rate of $10 to $20, depending on club, and will provide intermittent access during fall, winter, and spring break periods from September 1 to April 30.

                        26 and Under Membership Details

                        Discounted monthly rate for access to one club. Individual must be at least 12 years but less than 27 years of age. When member reaches age 27, this membership will automatically be converted to the then-prevailing individual membership rate at the applicable club membership level.

                        Junior Executive Membership Details

                        Discounted monthly rate for individuals at least 12 years but less than 30 years of age. When member reaches age 30, this membership will automatically be converted to the then-prevailing individual membership rate at the applicable club membership level.

                        Membership dues, levels, fees, benefits, services and amenities vary by club and are subject to change at any time. Other terms and conditions apply. *Show additional Monthly, 26 and Under, Student, and Day Pass terms and conditions.

                        Monthly memberships are month-to-month access memberships that continue until canceled upon 30 days’ advance written notice.
